# Daily Journal System - Git Ignore
# Protects your personal journal entries while preserving folder structure

# Personal Journal Entries (exclude all actual entries)
journal/daily/entries/*.md
journal/daily/reflections/*.md

# Keep the folder structure visible (don't ignore .gitkeep files)
!journal/daily/entries/.gitkeep
!journal/daily/reflections/.gitkeep

# Allow example files to be shared (for documentation)
!journal/daily/entries/EXAMPLE-*.md
!journal/daily/reflections/EXAMPLE-*.md

